MAN/READERS MANUAL Entry for 'var':
******************************************************
FUNCTION: [var]

Description
Creates a new empty variable or multiple empty variables, the function is variadic in nature

General Syntax
::*var, *var, *var...

*var     = var may be replaced with the name of the variable you would like to create. Scorpion creates the variable in question

Example:
var::*car, *truck, *bus

See Also
varset, vardelete, vartag
